<p>Because the pricing data here is reported by players and unreliable at best.  Sometimes people put in high prices to increase the precieved value because they have one to sell, but in most cases it is high because it includes dated (i.e., old) data.  If you look at the details of the price you will notice the inflation comes from price estimates put in over a year ago.  The last 2 prices submitted are 500pp and 750pp which is more in line with current prices following SoV and SoL.</p>
