<p> Excellent cloak. Some nice AC (for a cloak) +5 Str (every 5 points in a stat, you hit a milestone where they become more efficient) and +45 HP which at higher levels may seem like nothing (You are hit for 200 damage) but coupled with any other items you have chanced upon, that can be extremely effective. It gives you the 3 most important stats to most melee (if not all). AC, Str, and HP are top priority, bar none. Get this item, now!</p>
